      "raw_text": "Having come to the conclusion\nthat irrigation Is needed to bring\nout the full productiveness of its\nfarm holdings west of the city, the\nHazelwood company is preparing a\nbig scheme, which contemplates\ntaking water from Silver lake and\nirrigating about 1000 acres recent\nly cquired by the company. A\npumping plant with triple the ca\npacity of the system of the city\nof Spokane Is being planned."
